{"tid":174330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（支爆）人行樊綱：外儲降至2萬億美元可能是好事","createTime":"2017-03-26T16:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T01:35:49.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"081c6701b1e95b7a8c78a558f3f158837bc36a5e","tid":174330,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"央行貨幣委員會樊綱：<br />\r\n外儲降至2萬億美元可能是好事<br />\n<br />\n2017-03-25 16:45<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\n週六，央行貨幣政策委員會委員、 國民經濟研究所所長樊綱在博鰲亞洲論壇2017年會的分論壇中指出&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n\r<br />\n以下為樊綱講話要點：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n        從穩定國際收支的角度來講，<span style=\"color: red;\">央行並不願意擁有4萬億美元的外儲，降到2萬億美元可能是很好的事情</span>。但不希望看到波動在一夜之間發生，希望平穩過渡和調整。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n        <span style=\"color: red;\">經濟高增長並不意味著健康</span>。現在是在處理過熱經濟的後果，政府人員其實比較放鬆，只要經濟穩定增長、不再下滑，如今的增長率也還不錯。<br />\r&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n\r<br />\n<a href=\"http://wallstreetcn.com/articles/297173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwallstreetcn.com%2Farticles%2F297173&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7e541845\" target=\"_blank\">http://wallstreetcn.com/articles/297173</a>"},{"pid":"21a2d33c0aac56aa3af2d96b30de31c9d238acbe","tid":174330,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"降到1萬億果陣會話2萬億太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd6fe0e094b1c552309ff90b14aae90f41e9158","tid":174330,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>降到1萬億果陣會話2萬億太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實儲錢備要搵地方擺會造成不必要支出"},{"pid":"9cb45cd13145b73bfefa1ae8da004a6e517da907","tid":174330,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>降到1萬億果陣會話2萬億太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實儲錢備要搵地方擺會造成不必要支出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n使晒去最好"},{"pid":"e89e00545f0dc8197dd5620a21b829d5549b18bc","tid":174330,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"中國終成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b0f313669446f698f41d92521203801e72863e","tid":174330,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:19:11.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n反正最後贏的一定是中國"},{"pid":"b7f7e379d2753186a7f969c9a61e17909229a57d","tid":174330,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:32:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15f8dda660e5dba8151f6945bb156e7086194006","tid":174330,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T20:34:43.000Z","msg":"一年前先話仲有3萬億 一年內已經降到2萬億 睇怕支爆應該2年內發生"},{"pid":"0dd72af759d9eeb007d40f4bd0676ded7b52e44d","tid":174330,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T20:48:48.000Z","msg":"留名睇支那自己印美金"},{"pid":"c38ca0520e2cecdb46d7e7c3c95e30c91e924869","tid":174330,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T22:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇支那自己印美金</blockquote><br />\n北泡菜已經做呢樣野啦好似"},{"pid":"90f6637c0208d70cb29b9b0dc531dc348fe95fe5","tid":174330,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T22:57:26.000Z","msg":"中國又係最大贏家"},{"pid":"3419b1831424f4f5e6b340abb2a9a3eee667461c","tid":174330,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:22:43.000Z","msg":"2萬億》1萬億》0 好事"},{"pid":"ea041842812a41fa8f0a0c42bb5ab4e50a767611","tid":174330,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"幾時講：支爆可能係好事"},{"pid":"7b1dafc68229e2eeceb5f12968a36252bfd4b590","tid":174330,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"咁都叫支爆?"},{"pid":"c4b9ae116c2e376113cbd